      "text": "During the [[Welcome to Applied Fiction]] exhibition by [[Jean-Pierre Bekolo]], you have the opportunity to experience the first writing platform of the future for filmmakers where writing is no longer separate from making. This future narrative platform allows a group of people to write a screenplay the same way they interact on social media -- with the possibility for everyone to get credited and paid for each single word they have contributed."
